headline: Equifax and Qlarifi Partner to Study Impact of Buy Now, Pay Later on Credit Risk and Fraud
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) a global data, analytics and technology company, and Qlarifi, the first real-time consumer credit database purpose built for Buy Now, Pay Later lending, are partnering to conduct a joint study on the impact of BNPL reporting on credit risk assessments and fraud prevention.
